snippet.title: tomorrow is my birthday [launch trailer]
snippet.description:
follow Petal and Bios while they are running away from home.
two best friends who strive to be a person.
driven by a horrible secret.

and ask yourself: "we don't have to do this. why don't we just leave?" a point-and-click-adventure for those who dare to answer this question truthfully.

play tomorrow is my birthday on itch: lemonblood.itch.io/tomorrow-is-my-birthday
or steam: store.steampowered.com/app/2940020/tomorrow_is_my_birthday/

Created by: rileylessthan9
Music: Polygon Cove
Artwork: stargrrl
Voice Acting: Valentin Räber
